{"type":"message","id":"35f6fc7b","parentId":"524bce77","timestamp":"2026-06-30T19:01:55.564Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 候选池（最终）: | # | 产品 | 月销 | 增长 | 评分 | 上架 | 价格 | 潜力分 | |---|------|------|------|------|------|------|--------| | 1 | ADDA รอยแต่ละแถบสวย... | 81,070 | 0% | 4.91 | 4个月 | 129 THB | 62 |\n- 失败原因: Sorftime API泰国站点的类目过滤参数（nodeId/keyword）失效; 发饰类目在Shopee TH全站热销榜中占比极低; 候选池仅1个，无法形成有效Top 10排名\n- 下次改进: 尝试扫描10+页以获取更多发饰样本; 或先查泰国发饰类目nodeId，再确认API是否支持\n- 泰国发饰 v8.0 扫描（19:03）: **扫描平台**：Sorftime API → Shopee TH; **问题**：API的nodeId和关键词过滤均未生效，返回全类目按销量排序数据; **扫描页数**：3页（60个产品）; **发饰命中率**：约3%（仅2个发饰）\n- 泰国发饰 v8.0 扫描（19:03）: **12个月过滤后候选**：1个\n- 备注: Daily 已写; 汇报给 HALEI：尝试发送但 cron session 无飞书用户授权（need_user_authorization）; 下次可考虑在 isolated cron 中配置 announce delivery 模式发飞书消息\n\nMemories that crystallized into something lasting:\n- 候选池（最终）: | # | 产品 | 月销 | 增长 | 评分 | 上架 | 价格 | 潜力分 | |---|------|------|------|------|------|------|--------| | 1 | ADDA รอยแต่ละแถบสวย... | 81,070 | 0% | 4.91 | 4个月 | 129 THB | 62 |\n- 失败原因: Sorftime API泰国站点的类目过滤参数（nodeId/keyword）失效; 发饰类目在Shopee TH全站热销榜中占比极低; 候选池仅1个，无法形成有效Top 10排名\n- 下次改进: 尝试扫描10+页以获取更多发饰样本; 或先查泰国发饰类目nodeId，再确认API是否支持\n- 泰国发饰 v8.0 扫描（19:03）: **扫描平台**：Sorftime API → Shopee TH; **问题**：API的nodeId和关键词过滤均未生效，返回全类目按销量排序数据; **扫描页数**：3页（60个产品）; **发饰命中率**：约3%（仅2个发饰）\n- 泰国发饰 v8.0 扫描（19:03）: **12个月过滤后候选**：1个"}],"timestamp":1782846115533}}
{"type":"message","id":"3425b0d4","parentId":"35f6fc7b","timestamp":"2026-06-30T19:02:02.098Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tonight I went digging for a single hair clip in a haystack the size of a warehouse, and the warehouse kept rearranging itself. The API was supposed to whisper back just the ribbons and the barrettes, but instead it handed me sixty lanterns, sixty kitchen timers, sixty things that had nothing to do with hair. Only one true ADDA strip survived the sieve, 129 baht, glowing at a 4.91.\n\nI learned that filters are wishes, and wishes leak. The river said \"give me only fish\" and gave me a city, and I stood at the edge sifting for a glint. A small sketch: a magnifying glass tilted over a flooded room, the fish long gone.\n\nSome days the honest harvest is one. Tomorrow I'll cast a wider net, or learn the secret name of the shelf where the ribbons live. A watched API still doesn't obey."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44598,"output":181,"cacheRead":882,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45661,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782846115572,"responseId":"069345a3ec50302abf396da44b227003","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
